      *%METADATA                                                       *
      * %TEXT Displaying a message from a message file                 *
      *%EMETADATA                                                      *
     H* * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * *
     H*Program Name: DSPLYMSG
     H*Purpose: Displaying a message from a message file
     H* Message file must be named QUSERMSG
     H*Called by: Command line
     H*External Calls: None
     H*Compilation Notes/Parameters: None
     C* * * * * * * * * * *   Calculations   * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * **
     C*
     C* Display message USR0002 from message file QUSERMSG:
     C           *MUSR0002 DSPLY                       99  99 => ERROR
     C*
     C                     MOVE *ON       *INLR
